Finance Buddy
=============

Your AI-powered personal finance companion designed for young adults and beyond.

Overview
--------
Finance Buddy is an application that helps users learn about personal finance,
build smart budgeting habits, and navigate the stock market with confidence.
An AI buddy guides you through every decision — explaining the "why" so you
grow your knowledge alongside your portfolio.

Features
--------
- Financial Education: Interactive lessons on investing, budgeting, and
  financial literacy tailored to your knowledge level.

- Budgeting Tools: Create and manage budgets, track income and expenses,
  and get tips to improve your spending habits.

- Stock Market Guidance: Learn to read stock charts, understand market
  indicators, and interpret financial news with real-time data.

- AI Portfolio Manager: Your AI buddy monitors the market during trading
  hours and prompts you with buy/sell recommendations. You always get a
  clear explanation and the final say — accept, deny, or ask questions.

- AI Chatbot Companion: Name your Finance Buddy during onboarding and
  chat with it anytime. Ask about financial concepts, your portfolio,
  money advice, or anything finance-related — even when the buddy isn't
  actively managing your portfolio. A friendly animated avatar/mascot
  will accompany the chat interface in a future update.

- Personalized Recommendations: Receive suggestions for stocks, funds,
  and strategies based on your goals and risk tolerance.

Who Is It For?
--------------
- Primary audience: Young adults ages 16-25 new to personal finance.
- Open to users of all ages looking for an accessible financial companion.
- Users must be 16 years or older to create an account.

Key Principles
--------------
- Education-first: Every recommendation is a learning opportunity.
- Transparency: The AI always explains its reasoning.
- User control: You approve every transaction.
- Accessibility: Simple language and intuitive design for all experience levels.

